@Thomasmisfit , you could use the following and use a config file. We support boto, s3cmd and aws credential files.

![screen shot 2015-11-02 at 9 40 52 am](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1518713/10889269/dd0c7b38-8145-11e5-8918-38f81e8ec4c3.png)

Or you could also enter the access and secret key in the extra field. The keys have to be named `aws_access_key_id` and `aws_secret_access_key`.
